---
title: Picnic Pulled BBQ Chicken Sandwiches with Slaw, Pickled Jalapeño & Potato Wedges
description: Nothing says summer quite like outdoor eating, and these BBQ pulled chicken sandwiches are perfect for just that. Everything comes together in just 30 minutes—while you roast a side of potato wedges, you’ll pickle your jalapeño, mix your coleslaw, and heat up your chicken. Pile it all onto toasted potato buns, then dig into a saucy, summery feast that’s perfect whether you’re dining al fresco or bringing the picnic indoors.
